Bola Tinubu And Governor Abdullahi Ganduje The Governor of Kano state, Abdullahi Ganduje has paid a courtesy visit to the national leader of the All Progressives Congres, Bola Tinubu in Lagos state. However, the purpose of the meeting was not made public. H E @GovUmarGanduje last night paid a visit to the National Leader of the @APCNigeria, Chief Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, at his residence in Lagos. pic.twitter.com/3acVvqZKNG A Twitter user who was at the event shared the photos and wrote: “H E @GovUmarGanduje last night paid a visit to the National Leader of the @APCNigeria, Chief Asiwaju Bola Ahmed Tinubu, at his residence in Lagos.” See more photos below: Source